_sText:
!ALL BUGS HAVE BEEN FIXED!
This is my first Deathrun map, and people seem to like it actually, I had a lot of problems while making this map, it tooked one week to finish it :P I added some dustmotes just to create a better ambience, with a nice sky. Credits: - All the guys who helped me with some problems; - All deathrun mappers for the trap ideas; - All the beta testers Killa and Pingo_tinto; - To me for being a great inspiration. 14 controlled traps, and 4 non-controlled.____ 1st trap: The STBU [The Stupid Trap By Unreal] ______________________________________________ 2nd trap: Lasers of dooom! ______________________________________________ 3rd trap: The three Things. ______________________________________________ 4th trap: Smashing to the sky. ______________________________________________ 5th trap: The Kooolest! ______________________________________________ 6th trap: ElectraFutation. ______________________________________________ 7th trap: The Pusha! ______________________________________________ 8th trap: ?Random. ______________________________________________ 9th trap: n00bDown. ______________________________________________ 10th trap: Lift of lol. ______________________________________________ 11th trap: Fan of dooom! ______________________________________________ 12th trap: Spikes of dooom! ______________________________________________ 13th trap: BlindCortez. ______________________________________________ 14th trap: THE LAST! ______________________________________________ I Hope you like it guys, play it and have fun. Don't forget this is the test version. Please tell me if you find any problem with it. I would like to know if you run it on your server.
